gue in for the acting class, like after that, a whole process, and it was\n\n53:51.800 --> 53:58.160\nlike this tough guy, asshole, like, like kind of a mean, angry monologue, and I was trying\n\n53:58.160 --> 53:59.160\nto be a tough guy.\n\n53:59.160 --> 54:01.720\nAnd he goes, okay, Jeff, that was good, let's do it again.\n\n54:01.720 --> 54:06.280\nAnd you have your card up, you're placard with all your essences on it, which is, you\n\n54:06.280 --> 54:11.640\nknow, kind of like, you feel very exposed, because you're proud of some, embarrassed\n\n54:11.640 --> 54:14.120\nby others, but they're there.\n\n54:14.120 --> 54:20.320\nAnd he goes, Jeff, why is, because one of my essences was dashing, pardon, dashing.\n\n54:20.320 --> 54:22.240\nIt gets you choked up how dashing you are.\n\n54:22.240 --> 54:23.240\nNo, sorry.\n\n54:23.240 --> 54:24.240\nSee?\n\n54:24.240 --> 54:26.440\nIsn't that dashing him?\n\n54:26.440 --> 54:28.120\nAnd he goes, Jeff, why is dashing on that?\n\n54:28.120 --> 54:29.120\nI go, I don't like that one.\n\n54:29.120 --> 54:32.720\nThat's why, because someone, someone that's dashing wouldn't say they're dashing.\n\n54:32.720 --> 54:34.680\nAnd he goes, do it again.\n\n54:34.680 --> 54:41.000\nAnd I did it as dashing, you know, and it was way scarier, like, like, if you just like\n\n54:41.000 --> 54:42.320\nown anything.\n\n54:42.320 --> 54:47.360\nHe told one guy, he goes, do it again, but sit on your hands.\n\n54:47.360 --> 54:50.160\nHe goes, you can't use your hands, now do it.\n\n54:50.160 --> 54:53.080\nAnd it was the most terrifying thing in the world.\n\n54:53.080 --> 54:58.040\nHe just had this way to bring out something by the turn of your hat, or a little thing.\n\n54:58.040 --> 55:03.200\nOr like, if it was Randy, and you go, do it, like, see the way you're tilting your head?\n\n55:03.200 --> 55:06.680\nLike, why do you, like, why do you do that?\n\n55:06.680 --> 55:08.240\nI always do it.\n\n55:08.240 --> 55:09.240\nNow start.\